reviewText: Di Di Hollywood(2011) is a tacky soap opera!  It's about a barmaid from Spain who wants to be a movie star in Hollywood. She's willing to do unpleasant things. I laughed my butt off when the Maria character got run over by a car! "My Maria...got crushed by a car..."  The female lead has no charisma! What is Peter Coyote doing in this movie? This is an R rated film. There is nudity in it. This dumb, vapid movie is a waste of time!

Well this is a story that has been told over in many ways over the years. but this one is from a Latino perspective. I enjoyed it even though it was a bit B grade, at the right price with nothing else on, buy it and enjoy.

In the beginning, the film was boring, annoying and unbelievable, then it just dragged on and on.  There could have been a story there, but not here.  None of the characters were developed and were all very one-dimensional.  The acting was poor as well.  What a disappointment!
